  scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs,project,Bound the unresolved-error query to a sentry-window-days recent-activity window
  scripts/release/run-gates.mjs,project,Thread sentry-window-days through to the gate
  .github/workflows/release.yml,project,Invoke gate with explicit sentry-window-days 14
  .github/workflows/auto-release.yml,project,Open or update Auto Release blocked GitHub issue on scheduled failure
close_reason: "Durable fix shipped: recent-activity window on the Sentry gate + blocked-release alerting; verified live and at 100% coverage."
